implements org.eclipse.swt.events.PaintListener, org.eclipse.swt.events.ControlListener, org.eclipse.swt.events.MouseMoveListener, org.eclipse.swt.events.MouseListener

Tree map UI widget. It displays information represented in a IWeightedTreeModel as a tree map and supports navigation inside of the model.
